==体重范围==
大猫的体重范围很大。成年雪豹体重一般为{{Convert|22|to|55|kg|lb|abbr=on}}，个别物种可达{{convert|75|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref name=WCoW2002>{{cite book |author=Sunquist, M. |author2=Sunquist, F. |year=2002 |chapter=Snow leopard |title=Wild Cats of the World |publisher=University of Chicago Press |location=[[芝加哥|Chicago]] |pages=[https://archive.org/details/wildcatsofworld00sunq/page/377 377–394] |isbn=978-0-226-77999-7 |chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=IF8nDwAAQBAJ&lpg=PP1&pg=PA378#v=onepage&f=false |url=https://archive.org/details/wildcatsofworld00sunq/page/377 }}</ref><ref name="Boitani1984">{{cite book |author=Boitani, L. |year=1984 |title=Simon & Schuster's Guide to Mammals |location= |publisher=Simon & Schuster, Touchstone Books |isbn=978-0-671-42805-1 |url=https://archive.org/details/simonschustersgu00boit }}</ref>，而猎豹的体重一般为{{convert|21|–|72|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref name="Estes">{{cite book |last1=Estes |first1=R. D. |title=The Behavior Guide to African Mammals: Including Hoofed Mammals, Carnivores, Primates |year=2004 |publisher=University of California Press |location=Berkeley, USA |isbn=978-0-520-08085-0 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/isbn_0520080858/page/377 377–383] |edition=4th |url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_0520080858/page/377 }}</ref>。

雄性和雌性狮体重一般分别为{{convert|150|-|249.5|kg|lb|abbr=on}}和{{convert|110|-|182|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref name="NowellJackson1996">{{Cite book |author1=Nowell, Kristin |author2=Jackson, Peter |title=Wild Cats: Status Survey and Conservation Action Plan |url=http://carnivoractionplans1.free.fr/wildcats.pdf |year=1996 |publisher=IUCN/SSC Cat Specialist Group |location=Gland, Switzerland |isbn=978-2-8317-0045-8 |pages=1–334 |chapter= |access-date=2020-05-04 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226123919/http://carnivoractionplans1.free.fr/wildcats.pdf%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nowak">{{Cite book |last=Nowak |first=Ronald M. |year=1999 |title=Walker's Mammals of the World |url=https://archive.org/details/walkersmammalsof0001nowa |location=Baltimore |publisher=Johns Hopkins University Press |isbn=978-0-8018-5789-8}}</ref>，雄性和雌性虎体重分别为{{convert|100|-|306|kg|lb|abbr=in}}和{{convert|75|-|167|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref name=Mazak1981>{{cite journal |author=Mazák, V. |year=1981 |url=http://www.science.smith.edu/msi/pdf/i0076-3519-152-01-0001.pdf |title=''Panthera tigris'' |journal=Mammalian Species |volume=152 |issue=152 |pages=1–8 |doi=10.2307/3504004 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309125526/http://www.science.smith.edu/msi/pdf/i0076-3519-152-01-0001.pdf |archivedate=2012-03-09 |jstor=3504004 |access-date=2020-05-04 }}</ref>。而在[[原野|原野]]生活的雄性狮和虎的体重非常大，超过{{convert|306|kg|lb|abbr=in}}<ref name="Wood1983">{{cite book |last=Wood |first=G. L. |year=1983 |title=The Guinness Book of Animal Facts and Feats |publisher=Sterling Publishing |isbn=978-0-85112-235-9 |url=https://archive.org/details/guinnessbookofan00wood }}</ref><ref name="UPOA1963">{{citation |work=University Press of Africa, with contributions from the Kenya National Chamber of Commerce & Industry |title=East African Business Digest |url=https://books.google.com/?id=i_JPAQAAIAAJ&q=TWO+mamuding+lions+which,+since+January+this+year,+killed+244+cattle+and+three+donkeys,+were+shot+at+lssuna+village+in+Tanganyika.+The+lions+were+found+to+weigh+700+and+800+lb.&dq=TWO+mamuding+lions+which,+since+January+this+year,+killed+244+cattle+and+three+donkeys,+were+shot+at+lssuna+village+in+Tanganyika.+The+lions+were+found+to+weigh+700+and+800+lb. |year=1963 |access-date=2018-03-18}}</ref>，而[[圈养|圈养]]的体重约为{{convert|1,000|lbs}}<ref name="Wood1983"/><ref name="LSPC1941">{{cite news |publisher=Leonard Scott Publishing Company |title=The Nineteenth Century and After |volume=130 |url=https://books.google.ae/books?id=ylEQAAAAIAAJ&q=Samson,+1,000-pound+African&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj_1r725vPZAhXCthQKHbZDBRwQ6AEIJTAA |year=1941 |access-date=2018-03-17 |archive-date=2018-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180317232611/https://books.google.ae/books?id=ylEQAAAAIAAJ&q=Samson,+1,000-pound+African&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj_1r725vPZAhXCthQKHbZDBRwQ6AEIJTAA |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

狮虎可以长得比狮子和老虎还要大，尤其是名叫“Nook”的狮虎，重达{{convert|550|kg|lbs|abbr=on}}<ref name="LigerFacts">{{cite web |work=Liger Facts |title=The Liger - Meet the World's Largest Cat |url=http://ligerfacts.org/ |accessdate=2016-07-17 |archive-date=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715034500/http://ligerfacts.org/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="LigerWorldNook">{{cite web |work=Liger World |title=Liger Nook - Liger Profile |url=http://www.ligerworld.com/nook-the-liger.html |access-date=2018-04-23 |archive-date=2018-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180423232529/http://www.ligerworld.com/nook-the-liger.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

